lead_paragraph: Hungarian Laszlo Cseh powered to a convincing victory in the men’s 200 metres butterfly at the European Championships on Thursday and appeared relaxed about the possibility of an Olympic showdown with his nemesis Michael Phelps.

headline.main: Hungary's Cseh Unfazed by Phelps Return After Euro Win
